title: OneKey® MLS Relaunches OneKeyMLS.com
description: OneKey® MLS has launched an enhanced version of OneKeyMLS.com, the consumer property search portal offering listings in New York City, Long Island and the Hudson Valley region from 45,000 subscribers and 4,500 participating offices in the New York regional coverage area. The new site features more in-depth residential and commercial listing data in all five boroughs of New York City, as well as on Long Island, in Westchester, Putnam, Orange, Rockland and Sullivan Counties.
author: Tricia Chirco
name: OneKey® MLS
